# API Behavior Doc – Definition of Done (Commerce)

Sau khi implement xong một feature trong `commerce-service`, **bắt buộc** tạo file API behavior doc tại:

```
docs/api_fe_behavior/commerce_api_fe_behavior/<FeatureName>-api-and-behavior.md
```

Ví dụ:
- `AddProductToCart-api-and-behavior.md`
- `CheckoutFromCart-api-and-behavior.md`
- `ProcessPayOSWebhook-api-and-behavior.md`

## Nội dung bắt buộc

```markdown
# <Feature Name> – API & Behavior

## 1. Business Goal
## 2. API Contract
- Method, URL: /api/v1/commerce/...
- Auth: Bearer JWT (required/optional)
- Params

## 3. Response – Success
## 4. Response – Error
| HTTP | code string | Mô tả |
| 400  | COMMERCE-400-VALIDATION | ... |

## 5. Business Rules
## 6. Edge Cases
## 7. Data Dependencies
- PostgreSQL table(s)

## 8. FE Integration Notes
```

## Definition of Done

- [ ] Code đúng architecture (delivery → application → domain → infrastructure)
- [ ] API envelope chuẩn (`docs/engineering_rules/api-standard.md`)
- [ ] Error code `COMMERCE-*`
- [ ] Unit test business logic chính
- [ ] Integration test cho API/DB khi cần
- [ ] File `docs/api_fe_behavior/commerce_api_fe_behavior/<Feature>-api-and-behavior.md` đầy đủ
- [ ] Không business logic trong Controller/DTO
